# The XMEML emitter only ever produces LF. Force the golden fixtures to stay LF
# in the working tree on every platform so the byte-exact diff gate is stable
# (the emitter output is LF; a CRLF checkout would mask real diffs were the test
# not LF-normalizing). Keep the test sources LF too for the same reason.
tests/fixtures/*.xml text eol=lf
tests/golden_xmeml.rs text eol=lf
